<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Egloffstein, Amtmann zu Forchheim</head><p>Der Rat bittet erneut um Ausfertigung einer Urfehde.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_531" id="265r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_531_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vom Eglofſtein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l2">Amptman cʒu vorcheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_531_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Her <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem fricʒ Strobell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener empoten habt / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l5">Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd</del> v̈mb die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l6">vrfeh vor empfolhen / vnd ſecʒen das aber auff ew / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l7">ſelber wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtet</expan> / vvie Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">tun </del> dem tun ſüllet / vnd biten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l8">vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol Jr verſorgt vns darynne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l9">vnd vvie es cʒu ende kum / das wöllet vns an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l10">vviſſen laſſen bey <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> boten / dem vvir das lon gern <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l11">vnd <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> auch das v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> / <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdıenen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_531_r1l12"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ıj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Symo<ex>n</ex>ıs</expan> et Jude Anno xij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_531" id="265r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vom Eglofstein, amptman czu Vorcheim </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, als ir
                        uns <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem Fricz Strobell,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener, empoten habt, das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen.</expan> Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erberkeit
                            <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache ümb die urfeh vor empfolhen und
                        seczen das aber auff ew, <expan>wan<ex>n</ex></expan> ir selber wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stet,</expan> wie ir dem tun süllet; und biten
                        und getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol, ir versorgt uns darynne und, wie es
                        czu ende kum, das wöllet uns an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief wissen
                        lassen bey <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> boten, dem wir das lon gern
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> auch das
                        ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> verdienen. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Symo<ex>n</ex>is</expan> et Jude anno xii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
